    <item>
      <title>韩国向越过边境的朝鲜军队发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/s-korea-fires-warning-shots-at-north-s-troops-crossing-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国军方称，周日数名朝鲜士兵短暂越境并撤退后，韩国军方发出警告射击，此举可能加剧世界上军事化程度最高的边境之一的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/s-korea-fires-warning-shots-at-north-s-troops-crossing-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:02:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯告诉士兵们要做好应对“更令人担忧”的威胁的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/marcos-tells-soldiers-to-prepare-for-more-worrisome-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯要求该国北方部队做好应对中国和台湾之间紧张局势的任何准备，同时警告该国面临“更令人担忧”的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/marcos-tells-soldiers-to-prepare-for-more-worrisome-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 01:58:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉马杜罗准备签署协议承认选举结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/venezuela-s-maduro-ready-to-sign-pact-to-recognize-vote-results-lx9ps6ei</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗愿意签署协议，承认下个月总统选举的结果，尽管民意调查仍然显示他落后于反对派鲜为人知的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/venezuela-s-maduro-ready-to-sign-pact-to-recognize-vote-results-lx9ps6ei</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 01:19:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡加强对家族办公室和对冲基金的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/singapore-ramps-up-scrutiny-of-family-offices-hedge-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列丑闻凸显新加坡监管存在漏洞之后，新加坡当局要求家族办公室和对冲基金提供更多信息，同时加大对休眠公司的关闭力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/singapore-ramps-up-scrutiny-of-family-offices-hedge-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 00:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>辞职法官警告香港法治面临“严重危险”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/top-hong-kong-court-loses-third-overseas-judge-as-scrutiny-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，一位从香港最高法院辞职的英国著名法官对中国打压异见人士的做法提出了严厉批评，警告称，香港这个金融中心的法治面临“严重危险”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/top-hong-kong-court-loses-third-overseas-judge-as-scrutiny-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 18:39:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪选择内阁中熟悉的面孔以保持政策稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/india-reappoints-nirmala-sitharaman-as-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪保留了财政部等几位重要内阁部长的职位，这表明执掌全球增长最快的主要经济体的新联合政府将保持政策的连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/india-reappoints-nirmala-sitharaman-as-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 14:12:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
